The paper deals with texture classification, which is a common problem in computer vision and falls under the category of computer vision (cs.CV). The use of statistical features and analysis of primitive pattern units also suggests that the paper could fall under machine learning (cs.MM) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The use of color images and analysis of RGB channels suggests that the paper could also fall under image retrieval (cs.IR) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories.
